nodes.name: The Vestiges of Tukushapal
nodes.summary: This mod completely rebuilds and vastly expands the vanilla dungeon combo of Marvani Ancestral Tomb and Tukushapal. Embark on an adventure through water and fire to find the legendary Face of God as well as an ancient weapon that has the

nodes.name: The Wake of Hanin - Ibar-Dad Overhaul
nodes.summary: The Wake of Hanin overhauls and expands the vanilla dungeon of Ibar-Dad. Venture into the unfathomable depths of Ibar-Dad and solve two quests to find Mordrin Hanin's burial chamber and claim all its treasure for yourself!

nodes.name: Drethos Ancestral Tomb
nodes.summary: This mod adds a new dungeon to the Bitter Coast Region: Drethos Ancestral Tomb. Ancient and forgotten, it hides a sad story about loss and grief. Will you find your way through root and rock to uncover both it and an old and forsaken

nodes.name: Heran Ancestral Tomb Overhaul
nodes.summary: This mod overhauls and slightly expands Heran Ancestral Tomb. Made for the Summer Modjam 2023.

nodes.name: Caldera Priory and the Depths of Blood and Bone
nodes.summary: Caldera Priory has been overrun by the Undead. Do you have the courage and the will to venture into the Depths of Blood and Bone and vanquish the ancient Evil that has taken hold of the lands above?

nodes.name: Of Eggs and Dwarves - Gnisis Eggmine and Bethamez Overhaul
nodes.summary: This mod rebuilds and expands the Gnisis Eggmine complex from scratch, which includes the Eggmine, the Lower Eggmine, the Underground Stream, and Bethamez. It also adds a quest, which asks the player to investigate the origins of the

nodes.name: New Ilunibi
nodes.summary: This mod rebuilds the mainquest dungeon Ilunibi from scratch to make it larger, more imposing and more interesting to explore. It also adds four new quests for you to discover and embark upon.

nodes.name: ReadMe - Library of Vivec Overhaul
nodes.summary: This mod redesigns the Library of Vivec from scratch to make it look and feel like a true library, with many books added from Tamriel_Data and OAAB_Data for you to read. There are also new NPCs for you to interact with, and two new quests

nodes.name: Berandas Overhaul
nodes.summary: This mod overhauls and slightly expands the old Dunmer fortress Berandas near Gnisis. Daedra have claimed Berandas, but other than the few roaming Daedra themselves there is not much evidence of the corruption. With this mod, old daedric

nodes.name: A Walk in the Park - Mournhold Temple Courtyard Overhaul
nodes.summary: Overhauls those mostly empty green areas in Mournhold's Temple Courtyard by adding rocks, plants and some other stuff. The goal is to make those areas prettier and more interesting. Now they might actually be worth a visit.
